    <h3 class="text-center">Students Activities and Recreation</h3>
    <h4 class="text-center mb-30">(UCSI University Bangladesh Branch Campus)</h4>
    <p class="text-center mb-30">Dive into a world of student activities and recreation at UCSI University Bangladesh Branch Campus. Here, we believe that a fulfilling educational experience goes far beyond textbooks and lectures. We are proud to offer a vibrant and diverse range of student activities and recreational opportunities that foster a well-rounded and enriching campus life. Our commitment to holistic development is reflected in the exciting array of activities available to our students.</p>
    <p></p>
    <h4 class="text-center">Service</h4>
    <p></p>
    <p class="text-center">Oversee and provide guidance for the Extracurricular Learning Experience courses which promotes and encourages students to participate in activities beyond the classroom walls.</p>
    <p></p>
    <h4 class="text-center">Sports and Recreation</h4>
    <p></p>
    <p class="text-center">UCSI University Bangladesh Branch Campus is home to a thriving sports culture that caters to both sports enthusiasts and casual players. Whether you're a seasoned athlete or just looking to have fun, you'll find something to suit your interests. We offer popular games like 9-ball, karam, and table tennis, providing a fantastic outlet for friendly competition and relaxation. These sports not only promote physical fitness but also encourage social bonding and sportsmanship.</p>
